<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.3.2">
<l>uṭaiyār kaṉamaṇiyō ṭoṇmā tuḷampū</l>
<l>viṭaiviravik kōtta veḻiṟṟeḻki ṉōṭu</l>
<l>viṭaiyēṟu kāpāli yīcaṉ viṭutantā</l>
<l>ṉuṭaiyāy aḻēlaḻēl tālēlō vulaka maḷantāṉē tālēlō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Master, Śiva, the one who holds the skull, who mounts the bull,</l>
<l>sent a beautiful waist ornament that was strung [and] joined</l>
<l>in the middle of brilliant pomegranate flowers along with gold and sapphires.</l>
<l>Master, do not cry, do not cry, tālēlō! You who measure the earth, tālēlō!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
